data.description: Welcome home to this lovely 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch on 1.428 Acres with no HOA. Home opens into a living room. The kitchen includes a breakfast area, plenty of cabinet space, along with the dining area great for the family. Master on main along with 2 additional Bedrooms & Bath. Additional Bedroom/ Bath/ Bonus  upstairs. The private backyard offers plenty of space for kids to play or for entertaining guests and a shed. This home's Roof, HVAC, Septic, Hot Water Heater was replaced in 2021. Possible USDA 100% loan.  2 hours notice please, thank you for the understanding. Bring all offers.
